{
  "texts": [
    "For some aspects of OS, far fewer relevant articles were found.",
    "Three articles were identified as relevant to the societal impact of OS in general.",
    "One paper, by Zong et al.",
    "(218), indicated impact in terms of social engagement.",
    "The authors analysed articles from \"Psychological Science\" between 2014 and 2021, finding that Open Science badges were correlated with increased social media attention."
  ]
}